       Creates  a display file from an existing grid3 file according to speci-
       fied threshold levels.  The display file is a display list of  polygons
       that  represent isosurfaces of the data volume.  If specific _l_e_v_e_l_s are
       given, additional optional parameters are ignored.  _M_i_n or _m_a_x  may  be
       used  alone  or  together to specify a sub-range of the data.  The _s_t_e_p
       parameter is given precedence over _t_n_u_m.

